metadata.description:
# Punks Afloat

**Collection**: METAFASHION GM PUNKS!

**Rarity**: Rare


GM PUNKS life vest keeps you afloat in any crypto perfect storm, any metaverse. Bull or bear, just collect it - as the special patch says here. Surrounded by the positive and supportive GM ambience and decorated with PIXELORD GM Punks artwork (twice!). Comfy dark jacket with a blue plastic paint splash goes with colourful cropped slacks.

A metaversal NFT wearable inspired by the legendary PIXELORD GM PUNKS collection - designed and carefully tailored by @digital.fashion.princess and minted on ARTISANT. 

**Utility**: Wear it on your Ready Player Me avatar - wherever you like.
